{"prompt": "Build an intuitive platform for a virtual assistant company. The design should prominently display a soft periwinkle.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Virtual Assistant Platform</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #e6e6fa; /* Soft Periwinkle */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #d8bfd8; /* Lighter Periwinkle variant */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid #e6e6fa;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n        nav {\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #fff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #e6e6fa;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #e6e6fa; /* Soft Periwinkle */\n            color: #333;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #483d8b; /* Darker Periwinkle for contrast */\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n        }\n        .features {\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .features h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #483d8b;\n        }\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            color: #7b68ee; /* Medium Purple, complements periwinkle */\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n        }\n        .cta {\n            background-color: #d8bfd8; /* Lighter Periwinkle variant */\n            color: #333;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 50px 20px;\n        }\n        .cta h2 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #483d8b; /* Darker Periwinkle */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #6a5acd; /* SlateBlue, close to periwinkle family */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #483d8b; /* Darker Periwinkle */\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>AssistPro</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n                <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n                <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Your Reliable Virtual Assistant Partner</h2>\n            <p>Streamline your tasks, boost productivity, and reclaim your time with our expert virtual assistants. We provide comprehensive support tailored to your unique business needs.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"features\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Administrative Support</h3>\n                    <p>Email management, scheduling, data entry, document preparation, and more.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Customer Service</h3>\n                    <p>Handling inquiries, support tickets, live chat, and social media engagement.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Social Media Management</h3>\n                    <p>Content creation, scheduling posts, community engagement, and analytics.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Technical Assistance</h3>\n                    <p>Website updates, IT support, research, and online tool management.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Project Management</h3>\n                    <p>Task tracking, coordination, reporting, and deadline management.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Bookkeeping & Finance</h3>\n                    <p>Invoicing, expense tracking, basic payroll, and financial reporting.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"cta\" style=\"background-color: #e6e6fa;\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About AssistPro</h2>\n            <p>We are a team of dedicated and skilled virtual assistants committed to providing exceptional support to entrepreneurs and businesses of all sizes. Our mission is to empower you to focus on what matters most by handling your essential tasks efficiently and professionally.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"cta\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>\n            <p>Let us help you achieve your business goals. Contact us today for a free consultation.</p>\n            <a href=\"mailto:info@assistpro.com\" class=\"cta-button\">Contact Us Now</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 AssistPro. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple smooth scrolling for navigation links\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}